=E2=80=99s quote echoing Barry Diller=E2=80=99s famous response to losing P=
aramount to Sumner Redstone: =E2=80=9CThey won. We lost. Next.=E2=80=9D

=E2=80=9CThe Katzenberg comment is beyond. The Dems lost because Biden hung=
 around a year longer, if not more, than he should have. No one could enter=
 [the presidential race] and test themselves in an open primary process, wh=
ich may very well have yielded a better candidate. When many of us asked [J=
effrey,] =E2=80=98Is he okay? Can he do this?=E2=80=99 he assured us Biden =
was in top form. This we now know was absurd. So it=E2=80=99s fine for Barr=
y to say that line years ago about a deal! It=E2=80=99s another thing to pr=
etend you bear no responsibility for telling hundreds of
people, whose money you took, that all was well in the palace when you well=
 knew, given your proximity, that it wasn=E2=80=99t. Have a little integrit=
y, for God=E2=80=99s sake. =E2=80=98Let=E2=80=99s move on=E2=80=99 is a bit=
 cavalier, even for him.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94A producer

=E2=80=9CHappy for Jeffrey that he=E2=80=99s able to move on so easily. I w=
ish the thousands of women who are forced to give birth to nonviable fetuse=
s at great risk to their health were able to do the same.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=
=94An executive

=E2=80=9CThese. Fucking. Guys. Zaslav couldn=E2=80=99t wait at least a week=
 before he started trying to offload our company?=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94A Warne=
r Bros. employee

=E2=80=9CGood for Zaz, though. Pure private equity play to buy [Warner Bros=
=2E Discovery], strip it of assets, and=
 get paid out while a lot of people ne=
aring retirement or with newborns get laid off.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94Another e=
xecutive

=EF=BB=BF=E2=80=9CWe=E2=80=99re going to have to make these old executives =
retire. They've destroyed our industry in the
pursuit of endless M&A, and now they=E2=80=99ve enabled the rise of a digit=
ally savvy fascist regime. You don=E2=80=99t collaborate with Hitler and ge=
t to keep your conglomerate running.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94Another producer

Now Scott is here with his read on the =E2=80=98Wicked=E2=80=99/=E2=80=98Gl=
adiator=E2=80=99/=E2=80=98Moana 2=E2=80=99 smackdown over Thanksgiving=E2=
=80=A6

